print statements:

        System.out.println(): appends new line at the end

        System.out.print(): does not append new line at the end



Escape Sequences: MUST be used in ""

    \n: Enter key, starts a new line
    \t: Tab Key, starts a paragraph space
    \\: back slash
    \': single quote
    ': single quote
    \": double quote



\"   \"


